{"tid":1180488,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA 今日公開《仙劍奇俠傳七》即時光線追蹤技術展示影片","createTime":"2019-06-01T01:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T03:47:52.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4010e8160f18cac16a0a8bbcc14e2efdc3e5cb","tid":1180488,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:17:06.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA 與大宇資訊在今日 COMPUTEX 2019 展前記者會中宣布，知名角色扮演遊戲《仙劍奇俠傳》系列最新作《仙劍奇俠傳七》加入即時光線追蹤技術，並首度曝光技術展示影片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/88/eefa5ac4e1825857374215fdb314z805.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F88%2Feefa5ac4e1825857374215fdb314z805.JPG&h=a42adb46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA COMPUTEX 2019 展前記者會現場公開《仙劍奇俠傳七》即時光線追蹤技術展示影片"},{"pid":"bd475c15108262ec37f2ed3adbfdbc861abf7275","tid":1180488,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA 在今日記者會中，公開《仙劍奇俠傳七》支援即時光線追蹤技術展示影片，玩家可以從技術展示中看到洞穴石壁、地面水窪都忠實反射機關開啟後洞穴內的豐富細節，包括火焰綻放、岩漿滑落、香爐點燃等都即時加以反射，帶給玩家新的視覺體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/89/6fcf4df14bc406d9619259167e14z815.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F89%2F6fcf4df14bc406d9619259167e14z815.JPG&h=11a5c371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nw-46cZ0Utk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnw-46cZ0Utk&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=2bfb6a54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nw-46cZ0Utk</a><br />\n<br />\n大宇資訊表示，很感謝 NVIDIA 的大力支持，期待藉由此次雙方技術合作，能夠給《仙劍奇俠傳》系列不斷提昇產品品質的探索之路帶來新的指引，也期望未來能與 NVIDIA 達成更多技術合作。NVIDIA 則透露，他們也將與大宇資訊在《仙劍奇俠傳七》中進行更多的技術合作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/86/fe0d17caf805f57eafcbbf56bd14z7y5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F86%2Ffe0d17caf805f57eafcbbf56bd14z7y5.JPG&h=975db31f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/87/5c1bb3fdeebac6d7875aa08f9014z7z5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F87%2F5c1bb3fdeebac6d7875aa08f9014z7z5.JPG&h=868b7dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方提醒，此影片為雙方技術合作的技術展示影片，並非《仙劍奇俠傳七》實際宣傳影片。《仙劍奇俠傳七》尚未公布正式上市時程。"},{"pid":"e210bdc5cb6f6b0754986e1fb502be3d54383d1e","tid":1180488,"uid":71913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"好撚油膩"},{"pid":"adfc6d69859477c9190025e87a1a585e707c4e57","tid":1180488,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"整黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}